title: Live at the 2018 Skankfest with Tim Dillon and Ray Kump
description: Thank you for tuning in for another hilarious episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli.  This episode, our show is live from the 2018 Skankfest in Brooklyn.  Sam and Ryan welcome from the Tim Dillon Is Going To Hell podcast, Tim Dillion and Ray Kump.  The room was packed, the crowd was hot and the show was on fire!!!!  So enjoy the show and hopefully we will be doing more of these with Tim and Eddie Bravo in the future!!
